research_municipality_step.notes: The provided list of officials is based on the August 2025 City Council agenda and the Texas State Directory Online, which offer the most recent comprehensive rosters. While a Special Called Meeting in May 2024 mentioned Mayor Pro-Tem Berkley Beard, Alderman Wortham, and Alderman Bass in the roll call for newly elected officials, these individuals are not consistently listed in the more recent comprehensive council rosters used for this response. Mayor Pro-Tem Berkley Beard was also mentioned in an April 2024 agenda. Mayor Paula Eshelman and Alderman Danny Rambin (Position 5) were also referenced in a July 2024 news article.
